northeast , eastern thailand face sever drought thirteen provinc , mainli in northeast and eastern thailand , have been suffer a wors than averag drought sinc mid-februari and the dri spell is expect to last until earli may , deputi interior minist santi chaiviratana said . santi told report the govern is launch a drought relief oper mainli involv the use of water truck to send water to affect farm area . he did not say what crop have been damag in northeast thailand but said larg durian orchard in eastern chanthaburi provinc have suffer heavi loss . the minist said the affect area includ eight provinc in the northeast , two in eastern thailand and three rubber grow provinc in the south near the malaysian border .